      "span_text": "M. Tukalo we successfully crystallized one of the isoforms of mammalian factor  , and investigated the crystal structure of the naturally folded and post-translationally modified eEF1A2 × GDP complex from rabbit liver (Oryctolagus cuniculus) at 2.6 C resolution.",
